Here is a road map of the threadkit sources:

  src/core-threadkit	Contains the implementation of the threadkit features
			such as threads, channels, events, etc.

  src/glue		Contains code to glue the various threadkit parts together.

  src/OS		Contains a threadkit interface to the SML Basis OS API.

  src/IO		Contains a threadkit interface to the SML Basis IO API.

  src/Posix		Contains a threadkit interface to the Posix 1003.1a
			binding defined in the SML Basis. [not yet implemented]

  src/Sockets		Contains a threadkit interface to the SML Basis sockets API.

  src/unix		Contains a threadkit implementation of various Unix
			specific modules --- both internal and external.
